Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.50,0:03:59.08,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}許せば進めるし　恨みは立ち止らす
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.08,0:04:04.08,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}あれは僕のせいにしな　それも僕のせいにしてよ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.08,0:04:09.20,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}君をずっと立ち止める　その全てと
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.20,0:04:14.92,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}僕以外を許して　進んで行きなよ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.31,0:04:24.36,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}生涯枯れることのない花　と名付けても
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.36,0:04:29.47,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}生涯枯れることのない花　になることはない
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.01,0:04:34.58,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\3c&HDA7B00&}真面目に生きていれば　いつか報われる
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.04,0:04:39.62,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}そうやって言い切ってしまえば　それは嘘になる
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.62,0:04:44.69,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}身に起こるその数十％　自業自得でも
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.69,0:04:49.60,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}残りの数％　誰のせいでもないその不平等
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.60,0:04:59.68,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\3c&H1200FF&\t(2560,2810,\3c&H265CF5&)\t(3269,3519,\3c&HDA7B00&)\t(3603,3811,\3c&H47C73E&)\t(3937,4103,\3c&H5F2558&)\t(4437,4562,\3c&H386A2D&)\t(5396,5438,\3c&H1200FF&)\t(6189,6481,\3c&H45B6FE&,\bord0.8)\t(8274,8441,\blur0,\3c&H103568&,\bord2,\1c&HCCE1F4&)\t(8775,9275,\3c&H52164B&)\t(9359,9609,\blur3,\3c&H103568&)}一番いけないことはさ　自分はダメだと思うこと
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.68,0:05:04.68,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}あれは僕のせいにしな　それも僕のせいにしてよ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.68,0:05:09.72,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}僕以外を許して進んで行きなよ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.72,0:05:15.29,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}君自身のことも許してあげてよ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.72,0:05:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.50,0:03:59.08,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}寬恕促人前行 仇恨讓人停滯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.08,0:04:04.08,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}把那個當成我的錯吧 把這個也歸咎於我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.08,0:04:09.20,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}原諒讓你一直停滯不前之事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.20,0:04:14.92,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}原諒除我以外的所有人 前進吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.31,0:04:24.36,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}即便取名為永不凋謝之花
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.36,0:04:29.47,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也無法永不凋謝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.01,0:04:34.58,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\3c&HDA7B00&}認真活著就會有回報
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.04,0:04:39.62,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如此斷言的話語必定是謊言
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.62,0:04:44.69,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}百分之幾十是自作自受
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.69,0:04:49.60,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}剩下的百分之幾不怨任何人 如此不公
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.60,0:04:59.68,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\3c&H1200FF&\t(2560,2810,\3c&H265CF5&)\t(3269,3519,\3c&HDA7B00&)\t(3603,3811,\3c&H47C73E&)\t(3937,4103,\3c&H5F2558&)\t(4437,4562,\3c&H386A2D&)\t(5396,5438,\3c&H1200FF&)\t(6189,6481,\3c&H45B6FE&,\bord0.8)\t(8274,8441,\blur0,\3c&H103568&,\bord2,\1c&HCCE1F4&)\t(8775,9275,\3c&H52164B&)\t(9359,9609,\blur3,\3c&H103568&)}最糟糕的 是自我否定
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.68,0:05:04.68,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}把那個當成我的錯吧 把這個也歸咎於我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.68,0:05:09.72,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}原諒除我以外的所有人 前進吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.72,0:05:15.29,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也原諒你自己吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.29,0:05:17.29,op-cn,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.79,0:22:37.08,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}そうじゃない　求めるものは
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.08,0:22:41.63,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}強くこの手で掴もう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.72,0:22:54.27,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}泣いたって変わらないなら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.27,0:23:00.94,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}笑っても同じ　そう思っていた
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.94,0:23:07.57,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大事なものが守れないのは
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.57,0:23:14.54,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}弱い僕のせい　そう思っていた
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.54,0:23:20.25,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}どうして？　いま　ここに僕がいる理由は
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.25,0:23:23.66,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}誰が解らなくてもいい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.66,0:23:27.30,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}そう　君がいれば
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.30,0:23:34.06,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}見境無く燃える焔　 群衆が指をさす
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.06,0:23:37.77,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}僕はきっと強くなって　
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.77,0:23:40.69,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}誰だって守り抜く
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.10,0:23:44.07,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\c&HB54E25&\3c&HFFFFFF&}愛したいひとを想い　
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.07,0:23:48.78,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\c&HB54E25&\3c&HFFFFFF&}闇をこの手で払おう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.79,0:22:37.08,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不是這樣 追求之物
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.08,0:22:41.63,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要親手去緊握
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.72,0:22:54.27,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一味哭泣 則無法改變
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.27,0:23:00.94,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}強顏歡笑也一樣 我如此想到
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.94,0:23:07.57,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}無法保護珍視之人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.57,0:23:14.54,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是因為我太弱小 我如此想到
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.54,0:23:20.25,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}為什麼？ 我會在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.25,0:23:23.66,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}無人知曉也無妨
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.66,0:23:27.30,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只要有你在身旁
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.30,0:23:34.06,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}燃盡萬物的烈焰 飽受非議
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.06,0:23:37.77,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我一定要變強
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.77,0:23:40.69,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}保護所有人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.10,0:23:44.07,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\c&HB54E25&\3c&HFFFFFF&\b1}心懷所愛之人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.07,0:23:48.78,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\c&HB54E25&\3c&HFFFFFF&\b1}親手驅散黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.78,0:23:50.78,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.19,0:00:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}站 站住
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.18,0:00:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}拜託你了 奧村
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.58,0:00:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}希望你能用降魔劍打倒不淨王
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.53,0:00:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我知道這是個無理又勉強的請求
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.95,0:00:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但是如果 如果你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.50,0:00:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}能像你父親那樣對我施以些許慈悲之心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.48,0:00:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我想將希望寄託於你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.75,0:00:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}謝謝你看到最後 勝呂達摩
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.04,0:00:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}和我想的一樣 真是不得了的內容啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.20,0:00:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但是 雖然對不住勝呂同學的父親
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.82,0:00:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}哥哥的火焰對不淨王是否有效還只是推測
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.02,0:00:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不能因為這種不確切的事使用降魔劍
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.03,0:00:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}燐 這封信是寫給你的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.38,0:01:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你想怎麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.68,0:01:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.09,0:01:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}修拉小姐 你怎麼能問他呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.65,0:01:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我 我想幫他
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.93,0:01:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}哥哥 你知道自己現在的處境嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.65,0:01:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我也被老頭子救了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.55,0:01:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}所以 如果我能派上用場 那我也想去戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.08,0:01:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不過
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.06,0:01:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}當然 這只是我個人的意願
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.06,0:01:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那就要駁回你的請求…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.04,0:01:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.71,0:01:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}降臨於此 回歸於彼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.08,0:01:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}修拉小姐 你要做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.05,0:01:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}還能做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.60,0:01:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}他說要戰鬥 但不清楚他的狀態我可沒法批准
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.08,0:01:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就在這裡拔出來試試
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.10,0:01:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}修拉小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.25,0:01:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}哥哥才剛剛放出火焰胡鬧了一番
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.72,0:01:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}現在把降魔劍給他太不理智了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.39,0:01:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}要是再發生點什麼 肯定會被處刑的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.51,0:01:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.12,0:02:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我詠唱禁錮咒的時候梵蒂岡就已經知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.38,0:02:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}他們現在隨時都可能以此為由處決他
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.36,0:02:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}現在害怕也已經晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.12,0:02:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}而且這樣沒關係嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.92,0:02:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}如果不淨王復活 出現在了這個世界上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.80,0:02:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}現在它就比燐更危險
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.30,0:02:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}而且你也見過那麼多次了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.69,0:02:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}他的火焰對目前為止遇到的惡魔都有效
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.70,0:02:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}值得一試
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.31,0:02:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}燐 你拔出來試試
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.04,0:02:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.03,0:02:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}哥哥 你在做什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.79,0:02:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.51,0:02:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}拔不出來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.08,0:02:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.83,0:02:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不 不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.92,0:03:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不知怎麼回事 完全拔不出來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.45,0:03:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那我來幫你拔吧 給我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.64,0:03:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我自己拔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.12,0:03:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}大概是哪裡卡住了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.07,0:03:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}對 肯定是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.76,0:03:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.51,0:03:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.14,0:03:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}燐 你害怕了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.68,0:03:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不過這也很正常
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.19,0:03:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}剛剛才因為掌握了火焰而欣喜若狂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.11,0:03:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}然而轉瞬之間又回到了原點 你是這樣的心情對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.04,0:03:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}要是再拔出這把劍 我會怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.06,0:03:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}也許又會發狂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.82,0:03:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這次說不定真的會傷到其他人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.93,0:03:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這種事…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.34,0:03:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我說中了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.91,0:03:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你完全失去自信了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.75,0:05:24.55,biaoti,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fax-0.15\fad(0,518)\3c&HC4732D&\bord1.5\pos(1072,605)}氣焰萬丈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.98,0:05:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}等 等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.46,0:05:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}會因為這種事拔不出劍嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.70,0:05:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}哥哥 把劍還回來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.10,0:05:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這可真是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.10,0:05:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}晚上好 三位
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.99,0:05:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}菲雷斯卿
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.97,0:05:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}梅菲斯特 你來幹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.38,0:05:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這問法還真是沒禮貌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.51,0:05:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我時隔已久的登場居然是在監獄裡 我才失望呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.04,0:05:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真是的 虧我還是來給你們收拾爛攤子的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.96,0:05:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}1 2 3
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.88,0:06:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fnArial}Das stärkste Gefängnis
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.77,0:06:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}防禦力最高的牢房
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.54,0:06:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}梵蒂岡本部聯繫我了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.24,0:06:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}因方才詠唱禁錮咒之事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.33,0:06:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}經三賢者座下的審問委員會投票決定
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.85,0:06:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}處決奧村燐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.80,0:06:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}等 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.55,0:06:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}動作真快 這是真的假的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.84,0:06:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}都這種時候了 我可沒這閒工夫跑過來撒謊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.06,0:06:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}雪男 你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.65,0:06:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}比起這些事情 討伐不淨王才是當務之急
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.25,0:06:46.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不好意思 能幫我拿一下這個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.97,0:06:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你怎麼連這個都知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.62,0:06:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}既然這麼了解就來幫忙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.92,0:06:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.67,0:06:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不行的 我不擅長對付髒東西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.99,0:06:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}會過敏的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.65,0:06:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我的鼻子已經…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.83,0:07:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不淨王復活後會迅速成長
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.36,0:07:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}待它完全成熟之時 京都將化為一座死城
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.75,0:07:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我正帶著蝮趕回外派所 馬上就到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.27,0:07:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}請儘量讓大家都到門口來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.20,0:07:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你們那邊能看見嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.81,0:07:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}能看見嗎 蟒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.89,0:07:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那就是不淨王嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.63,0:07:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}討伐不淨王需要不少人手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.59,0:07:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}雖然只是些簡易的裝備
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.10,0:07:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我就送給你們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.43,0:07:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}希望這個能派上用場
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.58,0:07:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那麼 祝各位好運
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.76,0:07:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}喂 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.79,0:07:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那個混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.58,0:07:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}總之 我們先做力所能及的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.32,0:07:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.76,0:07:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我們應該也會被召集去討伐不淨王
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.71,0:08:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}外派所讓我們緊急集合
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.05,0:08:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}能動的人都去外派所
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.16,0:08:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.40,0:08:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}怎麼回事 外面好吵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.65,0:08:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是不是發生什麼事了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.09,0:08:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我聽說抓住蝮了 是真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.94,0:08:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是的 柔造正帶她回來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.66,0:08:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}抓住蝮了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.43,0:08:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}少住持
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.38,0:08:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}柔造回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.16,0:08:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}蝮 柔造
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.01,0:08:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}謝謝你把大家召集來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.62,0:08:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}大家 我是個叛徒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.86,0:08:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但是 還請大家聽我說幾句話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.17,0:08:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就在剛才 我和藤堂三郎太
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.74,0:08:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}用奪來的右眼和左眼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.69,0:08:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}復活了不淨王
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.92,0:09:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不淨王？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.24,0:09:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不淨王不是江戶時代就被打倒了的惡魔嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.80,0:09:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}它一直以假死狀態被封印在金剛深山的地下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.45,0:09:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}安靜點
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.62,0:09:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}現在明陀宗座主勝呂達摩大人 正留在那裡孤軍奮戰
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.71,0:09:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}請各位施以援手 打敗不淨王
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.66,0:09:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真 真是任性
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.72,0:09:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}明明你自己把它復活的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.95,0:09:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}再說了 不淨王到底是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.76,0:09:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}要怎麼打倒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.64,0:09:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}現在不是議論這些事的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.64,0:09:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}驅魔隊全體 巡邏一隊和二隊 以及深部一隊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.67,0:09:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}出發討伐不淨王
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.92,0:09:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不淨王是腐之王的眷屬
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.45,0:09:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}全員接種疫苗以抵抗瘴氣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.21,0:09:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}快去做接種疫苗的準備
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.58,0:09:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.49,0:09:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}蝮
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.75,0:10:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}龍 龍士大人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.39,0:10:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你的右眼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.39,0:10:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.58,0:10:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}請救救他 救救住持大人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.83,0:10:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}少住持 我帶她去醫務室
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.40,0:10:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}柔造 你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.72,0:10:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我稍後去和一隊匯合
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.52,0:10:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}少住持請務必和驅魔塾的各位一起回旅館
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.75,0:10:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}廉造 子貓
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.89,0:10:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}給我好好保護少住持
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.71,0:10:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}要是他出了什麼事 你們就等死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.34,0:10:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好好 交給我們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.40,0:10:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不用管我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.83,0:10:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}快去救住持大人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.50,0:10:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.65,0:10:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}她可是女人啊 藤堂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.79,0:10:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}少住持 這也沒辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.92,0:10:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}柔哥都那樣說了 我們就待在旅館吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.24,0:10:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.44,0:10:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你們過來一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.30,0:11:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}霧隱老師
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.06,0:11:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}由於剛才放出了火焰 燐的處刑決定了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.31,0:11:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這是梵蒂岡的決定 無法違抗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.53,0:11:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}然後
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.80,0:11:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}勝呂同學 這個暫時給你保管
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.36,0:11:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}俱利伽羅
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.89,0:11:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}還有你父親給燐的信
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.45,0:11:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}他說打倒不淨王需要燐的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.75,0:11:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}燐是想幫忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.19,0:11:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你們能把他救出來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.94,0:11:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}想讓燐免除處刑 就只能讓他將功贖罪了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.52,0:11:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}把這些迷彩斗篷拿去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.85,0:11:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}有隱身效果
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.22,0:11:45.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}應該能不被看守發現 接近他的牢房
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.19,0:11:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}霧隱隊長 請快一點
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.61,0:11:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.81,0:11:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就是這樣 說到底我也只是騎士團的狗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.88,0:11:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不能擅自行動
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.64,0:11:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}交給你們了 一切由你們自己判斷
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.16,0:12:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我們去救燐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.89,0:12:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那個
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.83,0:12:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}雖然很想去救他
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.29,0:12:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但這樣我們就是和梵蒂岡作對了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.44,0:12:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但 但是如果就這樣袖手旁觀 再也見不到燐了的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.01,0:12:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}大家一定會後悔的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.07,0:12:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}牢房在這邊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.86,0:12:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}少住持
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.73,0:12:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}勝呂同學 謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.48,0:12:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}子貓 你在開玩笑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.19,0:12:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}三輪同學
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.15,0:12:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我必須保護少住持
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.81,0:12:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}而且 我也一定會後悔的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.50,0:12:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}怎麼這樣 你就這麼怕柔哥嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.39,0:12:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}怎麼連出雲都這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.97,0:13:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}神木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.97,0:13:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}大家都怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.06,0:13:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}會死的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.27,0:13:06.76,zhu,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}別擋路廉造
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.20,0:13:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}小鬼回旅館睡覺去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.72,0:13:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我作為明陀的男人 死也要死得轟轟烈烈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.81,0:13:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.83,0:13:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}又是明陀又是後悔的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.53,0:13:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我真的不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.01,0:13:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真是的 麻煩死了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.17,0:13:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}痛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.80,0:13:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你剛才說話了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.89,0:13:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}沒有 是你說的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.78,0:13:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我什麼都沒說啊 是你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.12,0:13:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你少騙人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.00,0:13:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}嚇死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.40,0:13:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}都怪子貓踩到我的腳了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.59,0:13:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}原諒我吧 志摩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.66,0:13:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這個斗篷雖然很厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.68,0:13:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但是看不到對方也很麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.48,0:13:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}應該就在前面
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.20,0:13:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是那扇門嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.60,0:14:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}本大爺是{\fnArial}Das stärkste Gefängnis {\r\blur2}防禦力最高的牢房
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.86,0:14:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不過
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.62,0:14:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}雖然我無法從裡面被打開 但從外面就很容易
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.75,0:14:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那麼問題來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.32,0:14:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這是什麼角色
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.61,0:14:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}惡魔？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.63,0:14:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}為什麼說我防禦力最高呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.92,0:14:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}來攻擊本大爺試試吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.12,0:14:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}只能上了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.32,0:14:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}答案是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.96,0:14:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我能定住對本大爺抱有敵意的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.33,0:14:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這就是本大爺名字的由來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.66,0:14:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}怎麼會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.26,0:14:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}可為什麼我沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.09,0:14:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}因為你沒有敵意
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.22,0:15:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你很弱也沒拿武器
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.99,0:15:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}沒有了小尼 我真的一無是處
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.48,0:15:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.31,0:15:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}如果燐就這樣死了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.68,0:15:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我絕對不要這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.65,0:15:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}從外面可以打開門吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.93,0:15:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}當然可以 不過你就出不來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.84,0:15:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就算是為了大家 我也必須救出燐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.24,0:15:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這是什麼地方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.37,0:15:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我不能死在這種地方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.92,0:15:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我不能死
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.34,0:15:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真的是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.15,0:16:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你會老實等著被騎士團殺掉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.75,0:16:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}對了 還有自殺這個選項喔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.73,0:16:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你死了算了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.75,0:16:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不能讓大家救我的努力白費
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.89,0:16:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我一直是這麼想的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.02,0:16:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但是 說不定…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.82,0:16:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}要是再拔出這把劍 我會怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.22,0:16:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這次說不定真的會傷到其他人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.56,0:16:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我真的應該去死
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.34,0:16:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}還什麼忙都沒幫上 就要死掉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.27,0:16:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}到頭來 連跟大家和好都做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.64,0:16:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我到底是為什麼被救下來的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.94,0:16:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}老頭子 為什麼要救我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.00,0:16:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.56,0:16:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}燐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.57,0:16:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}詩惠美
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.96,0:16:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}燐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.48,0:17:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我來救你了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.19,0:17:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}霧隱老師把事情都告訴我們了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.74,0:17:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我們會和你一起戰鬥的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.76,0:17:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}快點從這裡出去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.38,0:17:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}別過來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.85,0:17:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.38,0:17:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我沒信心能控制住火焰
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.53,0:17:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我一直覺得可以靠氣勢來解決一切
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.87,0:17:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但這好像行不通
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.48,0:17:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我就這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.15,0:17:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}死了比較好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.32,0:17:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}什…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.61,0:17:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你在說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.65,0:17:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不准再說這種話了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.74,0:17:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.61,0:17:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}也不用懂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.17,0:18:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}別這樣 別這樣笑著疏遠我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.94,0:18:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我很想幫你的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.58,0:18:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你走吧 我是怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.27,0:18:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}一點都不燙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.65,0:18:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好溫暖
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.49,0:18:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我真傻
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.11,0:18:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}只想著自己
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.13,0:18:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}從沒認真關注過燐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.30,0:18:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這樣還算什麼朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.18,0:18:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}燐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.33,0:19:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.56,0:19:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}笨 笨蛋 你…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.57,0:19:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}危險
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.72,0:19:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.74,0:19:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你看 我根本就沒有被燒傷
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.52,0:19:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是你保護了我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.00,0:19:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}所以沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.40,0:19:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你不怕我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.94,0:19:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不怕
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.06,0:19:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是 是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.44,0:19:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}奧村同學
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.36,0:19:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}大家都是來救我的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.59,0:19:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我 我不想讓你死掉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.28,0:19:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}只要知道你沒有危險 我就會跟你和好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.20,0:19:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}子貓丸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.78,0:19:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我先聲明
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.25,0:19:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我只是聽從了霧隱老師的指示罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.07,0:20:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.78,0:20:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我可是很不想來的 表揚我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.57,0:20:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}大 大家
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.43,0:20:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}總之謝謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.39,0:20:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}勝呂… 同學
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.99,0:20:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}和老爸吵架的事確實是我不夠冷靜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.30,0:20:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你說得沒錯 僅限和老爸吵架的事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.20,0:20:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這是戰鬥要用的吧 拿著
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.60,0:20:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我 我才是 打了你對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.70,0:20:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我帶你去金剛深山
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.24,0:20:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}之後要怎樣隨你便
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.65,0:20:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我要用我的方式戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.38,0:20:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}勝呂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.60,0:20:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}相信我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.94,0:20:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}雖然身為撒旦之子的事實無法改變
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.56,0:20:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但我一定會把火焰控制好給你看
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.92,0:20:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}所以 相信我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.11,0:20:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那種事情怎樣都無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.28,0:20:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我之所以不能原諒你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.55,0:21:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是因為你把這些事全都悶在心裡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.26,0:21:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}什麼都不跟我們說
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.47,0:21:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你要我怎麼相信你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.53,0:21:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}難道只有我一個人覺得我們是同伴嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.80,0:21:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不 不是的 我不是那個意思
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.15,0:21:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}等等 就是因為這個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.12,0:21:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你生氣就只是因為這個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.33,0:21:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這原因真新穎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.24,0:21:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}志摩
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.23,0:21:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}勝呂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.47,0:21:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這樣啊 我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.28,0:21:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那麼 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.74,0:21:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}舞台和演員終於齊了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.73,0:21:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好了 就讓我盡情欣賞這場戰鬥吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.89,0:21:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}大家聽好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.10,0:21:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}目標是洛北的金剛深山
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.41,0:21:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}去打倒不淨王
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.99,0:22:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我只能用接下來的行動證明自己
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.79,0:24:05.34,zhu,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}第八集 父子相傳
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.77,0:24:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我是自願選擇現在這條路的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.04,0:24:10.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}跟爸爸和哥哥無關
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.89,0:24:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}
